        <mxCell id="summary-text" value="&lt;b&gt;File:&lt;/b&gt; models/base/model.py&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lines:&lt;/b&gt; 1,313 lines&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Total Methods:&lt;/b&gt; 40+&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Method Breakdown:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Initialization &amp; Properties: 6 methods&lt;br&gt;• Graph Building: 5 methods&lt;br&gt;• Backend Abstraction: 2 methods&lt;br&gt;• Table Access: 9 methods&lt;br&gt;• Join Utilities: 3 methods&lt;br&gt;• Metadata: 2 methods&lt;br&gt;• Measure Calculations: 4 methods&lt;br&gt;• Persistence: 1 method&lt;br&gt;• Python Measures Support: 1 method&lt;br&gt;• Extension Points/Hooks: 3 methods&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Key Features:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;✅ Backend-agnostic (Spark + DuckDB)&lt;br&gt;✅ YAML-driven graph building&lt;br&gt;✅ Lazy loading with caching&lt;br&gt;✅ Cross-model references&lt;br&gt;✅ Hybrid measures (YAML + Python)&lt;br&gt;✅ Dynamic joins via graph edges&lt;br&gt;✅ Extension hooks for customization&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Imports:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• abc (ABC)&lt;br&gt;• typing (Dict, Any, Optional, List, Tuple, Union)&lt;br&gt;• dataclasses (dataclass)&lt;br&gt;• pathlib (Path)&lt;br&gt;• logging&lt;br&gt;• pyspark.sql (DataFrame, functions) [optional]&lt;br&gt;• models.api.dal (StorageRouter, BronzeTable)&lt;br&gt;• models.base.measures.executor (MeasureExecutor) [lazy]&lt;br&gt;• models.api.query_planner (GraphQueryPlanner) [lazy]&lt;br&gt;• config.model_loader (ModelConfigLoader) [lazy]" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;fontFamily=Courier New" vertex="1" parent="1">
