        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="inheritance-text" value="All domain models inherit ALL methods from BaseModel and can:&lt;br&gt;• Override hooks: before_build(), after_build(), custom_node_loading()&lt;br&gt;• Add domain-specific methods&lt;br&gt;• Use inherited table access, measure calculation, persistence&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Implemented Models:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. CoreModel&lt;/b&gt; (models/implemented/core/model.py, 194 lines)&lt;br&gt;   + get_calendar(date_from, date_to, year, month)&lt;br&gt;   + get_weekdays(date_from, date_to)&lt;br&gt;   + get_weekends(date_from, date_to)&lt;br&gt;   + get_fiscal_year_dates(fiscal_year)&lt;br&gt;   + get_quarter_dates(year, quarter)&lt;br&gt;   + get_month_dates(year, month)&lt;br&gt;   + get_date_range_info(date_from, date_to)&lt;br&gt;   + get_calendar_config()&lt;br&gt;   &lt;i&gt;+ 40+ inherited from BaseModel&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. CompanyModel&lt;/b&gt; (models/implemented/company/model.py, 131 lines)&lt;br&gt;   + get_company_by_cik(cik)&lt;br&gt;   + get_company_by_ticker(ticker)&lt;br&gt;   + get_companies_by_sector(sector)&lt;br&gt;   + get_active_companies()&lt;br&gt;   + list_sectors()&lt;br&gt;   + get_company_count_by_sector()&lt;br&gt;   &lt;i&gt;+ 40+ inherited from BaseModel&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;3. StocksModel&lt;/b&gt; (models/implemented/stocks/model.py, 246 lines)&lt;br&gt;   + get_asset_type_filter() → 'stocks'&lt;br&gt;   + get_prices(ticker, start_date, end_date)&lt;br&gt;   + get_technicals(ticker, start_date, end_date)&lt;br&gt;   + get_stock_info(ticker)&lt;br&gt;   + get_stock_with_company(ticker)&lt;br&gt;   + get_stocks_by_sector(sector)&lt;br&gt;   + list_tickers(active_only=True)&lt;br&gt;   + list_sectors()&lt;br&gt;   + get_top_by_market_cap(limit=10)&lt;br&gt;   &lt;i&gt;+ 40+ inherited from BaseModel&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;   &lt;i&gt;+ Python measures: sharpe_ratio, volatility, beta, alpha, correlation, momentum&lt;/i&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Courier New" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1070" y="635" width="660" height="285" as="geometry" />
